TI  - The Purse Seine Fishing of Sardine in Portuguese Waters: A Difficult Compromise Between Fish Stock Sustainability and Fishing Effort
T2  - REVIEWS IN FISHERIES SCIENCE & AQUACULTURE
LA  - English
KW  - Purse seine fishery
KW  - sardine
KW  - stock assessment
KW  - fishing effort
