TI  - A win-win strategy for ecological restoration and biodiversity conservation in Southern China
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL RESEARCH LETTERS
LA  - English
KW  - biodiversity conservation
KW  - ecological degradation
KW  - livelihoods
KW  - poverty trap
KW  - social welfare
KW  - sustainable development
