TI  - Euros vs. Yuan: Comparing European and Chinese Fishing Access in West Africa
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - LARGE MARINE ECOSYSTEM
KW  - CLIMATE-CHANGE
KW  - FISHERIES
