TI  - Trees enhance soil carbon sequestration and nutrient cycling in a silvopastoral system in south-western Nicaragua
T2  - AGROFORESTRY SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Silvopastoral system
KW  - Leaf litter deposition
KW  - Soil carbon stabilization
