TI  - "The people here knew how I used to live, but now I have to start again:" Lived experiences and expectations of the displaced and non-displaced women affected by the Thwake Multipurpose Dam construction in Makueni County, Kenya
T2  - SOCIAL SCIENCE & MEDICINE
LA  - English
KW  - Dam-induced displacement
