TI  - Selection of new sweetpotato hybrids for West Africa using accelerated breeding scheme and genotype x environment interaction under drought stress
T2  - SCIENTIFIC REPORTS
LA  - English
KW  - YIELD STABILITY
KW  - AMMI ANALYSIS
