TI  - Modelling surface runoff using the soil conservation service-curve number method in a drought prone agro-ecological zone in Rwanda
T2  - INTERNATIONAL SOIL AND WATER CONSERVATION RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Available rainwater
