TI  - Toward an effective temporary fishing ban law enforcement in the Persian Gulf
T2  - MARINE POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Overfishing
KW  - Marine conservation
KW  - Fisheries management
KW  - Small-scale capture fisheries
KW  - COASTAL WATERS
