TI  - Impacts of stratospheric aerosol injection on the upwelling systems along the eastern boundaries of the southern tropical Atlantic Ocean
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL RESEARCH-CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - climate intervention
KW  - coastal upwelling
KW  - Angola-Benguela systems
