TI  - Seabird and marine mammal attendance in the Chub mackerel Scomber japonicus semi-industrial Argentinian purse seine fishery
T2  - OCEAN & COASTAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - WHITE-CHINNED PETRELS
KW  - LIONS OTARIA-FLAVESCENS
