TI  - Redefining pastoral vulnerability: A validated framework for livelihood assessment in climate-stressed dry rangelands
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL AND SUSTAINABILITY INDICATORS
LA  - English
KW  - Livelihood vulnerability index
