TI  - Spatial soil nutrient enrichment under Croton macrostachyus-based parkland agroforestry: Implications for sustainable soil fertility management
T2  - AGROFORESTRY SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Agroforestry systems
KW  - Land degradation
