TI  - Physiological responses and histological alterations induced by pollution in the Nile tilapia from the Rosetta branch of the River Nile, Egypt
T2  - SCIENTIFIC REPORTS
LA  - English
KW  - Nile tilapia
KW  - Histopathology
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Cortisol
