TI  - Fish Losses for Whom? A Gendered Assessment of Post-Harvest Losses in the Barotse Floodplain Fishery, Zambia
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - gender
KW  - post-harvest losses
KW  - small-scale fisheries
KW  - value chains
KW  - Barotse Floodplain
