TI  - Optimizing nitrogen application frequency to enhance the post-flowering matter accumulation, yield and water/nitrogen use efficiency of densely planted and drip-irrigated maize
T2  - JOURNAL OF THE SCIENCE OF FOOD AND AGRICULTURE
