TI  - Prospects for conserving freshwater fish biodiversity in the Anthropocene: A view from Southern China
T2  - INTEGRATIVE CONSERVATION
LA  - English
KW  - bending the curve
KW  - dams
KW  - micropollutants
KW  - non-native species
KW  - overexploitation
