TI  - Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities and Threats of Pasturelands in Terai Region of Nepal
T2  - JOURNAL OF LIVESTOCK SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - Forage production system
KW  - Livestock
KW  - Nutritional value
