TI  - Seasonal occurrence of Theileria parva infection and management practices amongst Maasai pastoralist communities in Monduli District, Northern Tanzania
T2  - VETERINARY PARASITOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Theileria parva infection
KW  - Prevalence
KW  - Seroprevalence
