TI  - Involvement of Women in Farm Decision-making and Adaptive Capacity to Extreme Events of Farming Households in Ligao City, Albay, Philippines
T2  - JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
