TI  - AGE, GROWTH, AND ABUNDANCE FLUCTUATION OF JORDAN'S DAMSEL, TEIXEIRICHTHYS JORDANI (ACTINOPTERYGII: PERCIFORMES: POMACENTRIDAE), IN THE SOUTHERN TAIWAN STRAIT
T2  - ACTA ICHTHYOLOGICA ET PISCATORIA
LA  - English
