TI  - TIJABAN-10 A DROUGHT TOLERANT AND HIGH YIELDING WHEAT VARIETY FOR RAINFED/SAILABA AREAS OF BALOCHISTAN
T2  - PAKISTAN JOURNAL OF BOTANY
