TI  - Agro-ecological options for fall armyworm (Spodoptera frugiperda JE Smith) management: Providing low-cost, smallholder friendly solutions to an invasive pest
T2  - JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Biodiversity
