TI  - Browse from Three Tree Legumes Increases Forage Production for Cattle in a Silvopastoral System in the Southwest Amazon
T2  - ANIMALS
LA  - English
KW  - agroforestry
KW  - silvopasture
KW  - sustainable
KW  - agriculture
KW  - livestock
