TI  - Sustainable dry forest management for cattle ranching: The effects of deschampado practices on the shrub layer and the light environment in comparison to roller chopping
T2  - FOREST ECOLOGY AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - semi-arid Chaco
KW  - shrub encroachment
