TI  - Optimal Control for Precision Irrigation of a Large-Scale Plantation
T2  - WATER RESOURCES RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - model predictive control
KW  - AquaCrop&#8208
KW  - OS
KW  - deficit irrigation
KW  - sugarcane
