TI  - Analysis of Spatial and Temporal Trends of Vegetation Cover Evolution and Its Driving Forces from 2000 to 2020-A Case Study of the WuShen Counties in the Maowusu Sandland
T2  - FORESTS
LA  - English
KW  - NDVI
KW  - spatial and temporal variations
