TI  - SRI as a methodology for raising crop and water productivity: productive adaptations in rice agronomy and irrigation water management
T2  - PADDY AND WATER ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Best management practices
KW  - Factor productivity
KW  - Roots
