TI  - Effects of flooding-induced migration on farm technical efficiency in Rivers State, Nigeria
T2  - JOURNAL OF AGRICULTURE AND FOOD RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Flooding
KW  - Migration
KW  - Crop output
KW  - Technical efficiency
